maman12

Class Point1

  • java.lang.Object
    • maman12.Point1

  • public class Point1
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a two-dimensional point on a grid in the first quadrant of the Cartesian coordinate system. The x and y coordinate values must be non-negative (positive or zero) integers.
